            "padding-inline-end": 0
          },
          "blocks": {
            "accordion_row_jzPz4J": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Will this fit in my car's cup holder?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_Tah4xq": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Yes! The tumbler is specifically designed with a tapered slim-base that fits most standard car cup holders, making it the perfect companion for your daily commute or long road trips.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "normal",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text_Tah4xq"
              ]
            },
            "accordion_row_LzbRGK": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Is the material safe and BPA-free?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_p6PK9g": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Absolutely. Our tumblers are crafted from high-grade 304 food-grade stainless steel. They are 100% BPA-free, lead-free, and rust-resistant, ensuring a clean and healthy drinking experience with no metallic aftertaste.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "normal",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text_p6PK9g"
              ]
            },
            "accordion_row_Vt8eFb": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "t:names.accordion_row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Does the lid prevent leaks?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_BgWT9d": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "name": "t:names.text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>The tumbler features a splash-resistant 3-in-1 lid. It includes a dedicated opening for the reusable straw, a wide-mouth opening for chugging, and a full-cover top to minimize spills while you're on the move.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "normal",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text_BgWT9d"
              ]
            },
            "accordion_row_iWKnw8": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "t:names.accordion_row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Is the tumbler dishwasher safe?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_yWCAPY": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "name": "t:names.text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>To preserve the premium matte finish and the integrity of the vacuum seal, we recommend hand washing your tumbler with mild soap and warm water. The straw and lid are top-rack dishwasher safe.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "normal",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
